(IC)<br>
<br>
This tale was told to me in a dream, by Quellious herself.  May her grace and love shine upon the Zan Fi, and upon Sister Aaia, and my friend Jagriel.<br>
<br>
To you, my friends, my family I kneel in humbleness.  I pay respect to thee and thy family in the traditional monk way.<br>
<br>
